---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Hero from '../components/Hero.astro';
---
<Layout title="Company Updates - Insight Hunter">
  <Hero />
  <section class="container">
    <p style="font-size:2rem; margin:60px 0 32px;">Company Updates and Announcements</p>
    <p>Stay informed with the latest developments from Insight Hunter. This section includes product releases, feature enhancements, and company milestones. Follow our journey as we innovate in financial intelligence.</p>
    <p>Recent updates: Released Insight AI v2.0 for improved query accuracy. Expanded Enterprise support to include custom workflows. Upcoming: Integration with more banking APIs and enhanced mobile features.</p>
    <p>Follow us on X for real-time updates:</p>
    <a class="twitter-timeline" href="https://twitter.com/yourusername?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw" data-height="600">Tweets by yourusername</a>
    <script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script> <!-- Replace 'yourusername' with actual -->
    <p>For archived news, visit the news page. Technical details on updates are in the tech section. Questions? See FAQs or contact us.</p>
  </section>
</Layout>
